cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper involves generating videos from text using a hybrid framework of VAE and GAN. It involves computer vision (CV) techniques for generating videos and natural language processing (NLP) techniques for processing text. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV. However, it also involves deep learning (DL) techniques, which fall under cs.LG and cs.AI. Additionally, it involves multimedia (MM) techniques for creating a matched text-video corpus. Finally, it involves language generation (CL) techniques for generating text-conditioned videos.
